Alpargatas to Open Havaiana Flip-Flop Shops in Europe, Independent Reports

-- B y   B r y a n   K e o g h
-- 
2011-03-06T09:37:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-06/alpargatas-to-open-havaiana-flip-flop-shops-in-europe-independent-reports.html
Havaianas, the Brazilian flip-flop
maker part of  Sao Paulo Alpargatas SA (ALPA4) , is planning to further
expand into  Europe  this year, opening shops in London, Paris,
Rome and Lisbon, the Independent on Sunday reported.  “We can sell our products not just in the summer and we
can prove this,” European president Eno Polo was quoted as
saying. Havaianas opened its first European outlet in Barcelona
last year, the Independent reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bryan Keogh in London at 
